The paper discusses planning and optimization of cellular networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization algorithms and spatial mappings, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper deals with the dynamics of service demand, which is related to control systems (cs.SY) and multimedia (cs.MM).
